1
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:09,359
I heard the Church of Light was robbed yesterday.

2
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:12,919
Three young men from the East stormed the temple

3
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,959
and caused chaos right under the noses

4
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:16,999
of a bunch of fifth-tier experts,

5
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:23,039
then escaped without a scratch.

6
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:25,279
We on the Western Continent

7
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:26,960
have grown far too reliant

8
00:00:27,080 --> 00:00:29,759
on energy-storing artifacts and magic crystals.

9
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:37,840
By the way...

10
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:41,399
Why did those three and the Dark Church suddenly attack the temple?

11
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,919
Spread the word and muddy the waters.

12
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,959
Say the two major churches clashed.

13
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,679
Claim the three Easterners

14
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:52,399
took advantage of the chaos to injure our temple mages.

15
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:54,600
Remember this:

16
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:57,039
Do not mention the divine bone under any circumstances.

17
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:58,800
Yes, sir.

18
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:01,920
One hundred and fifty thousand.

19
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,280
Two hundred thousand.

20
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,159
Two hundred and fifty thousand.

21
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,840
Meng Ke'er,

22
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:09,999
you'd better know when to stop.

23
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:11,679
Why should I let you—

24
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,519
You...

25
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,759
That divine bone is mine. I must have it.

26
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,480
You...

27
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,599
Don't... don't you dare—

28
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,759
The Huntian Dao is willing to offer three hundred and fifty thousand gold coins

29
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:42,639
to purchase this divine bone.

30
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,239
to purchase this divine bone.

31
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,520
Meng Ke'er,

32
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,079
don't force my hand.

33
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,239
The Tantai Sect offers four hundred thousand,

34
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:50,239
and no matter how much he bids,

35
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,679
I'm willing to add another fifty thousand.

36
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:53,719
You—

37
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,720
You...

38
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,559
Too many monks, not enough porridge.

39
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,160
In that case,

40
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,719
why not go rob a few more temples?

41
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,199
After this incident,

42
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,399
which empire's temple

43
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,039
do you think will unseal their shrine anytime soon?

44
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,960
Allow me to speak frankly.

45
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,079
Even if you obtain this divine bone,

46
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,319
you won't be able to wield the power within it.

47
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,080
What do you mean?

48
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,679
Before the God of Light was shattered,

49
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,479
he had already prepared for his resurrection.

50
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,519
He sealed his own power inside the divine bone.

51
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,559
How could any of you possibly refine it?

52
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,400
Stop trying to scare us.

53
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,800
If it's useless,

54
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,359
then why are you fighting over it?

55
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,639
I intend to place it within an array

56
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,239
to reinforce the seal on the devil inside our sect's secret realm.

57
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,920
What?

58
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,400
That devil...

59
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,879
is about to break free from the seal?

60
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,280
That's right.

61
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,119
The power of the seal has weakened considerably.

62
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,199
It must be replenished with divine power.

63
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,799
Otherwise...

64
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,359
once the seal breaks,

65
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,599
even the Huntian Dao won't be spared.

66
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,240
Don't forget,

67
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,799
back then, when our founding ancestor sealed that devil,

68
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,679
your Huntian Dao played a part as well.

69
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,719
The "devil" she's talking about...

70
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,919
Could it be the one we saw in the Void Heaven Illusion Realm?

71
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,959
So that's why she risked her life to seize the divine bone.

72
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,919
It was for this reason.

73
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,240
Dragon Baby,

74
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,520
give her the divine bone.

75
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,880
We're leaving.

76
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,480
Spit it out right now!

77
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,839
Damn it!

78
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,359
Baby is angry...

79
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,439
and the consequences...

80
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,640
Enough talk!

81
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,199
Spit out the divine relic!

82
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,720
Stop it, all of you!

83
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,640
How do you feel?

84
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,680
Is your body acting strange?

85
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,199
I feel something...

86
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,360
rolling around in my stomach.

87
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,999
Rolling... and rolling...

88
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,680
Dragon Baby...

89
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:10,839
Is Baby about to awaken his Heavenly Eye?

90
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,279
Why won't this thing leave?

91
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,559
Damn it, damn it!

92
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:20,080
Dragon Baby...

93
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:22,199
The God of Light's power has vanished.

94
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,880
Damn it!

95
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,079
That stupid dragon actually got the benefit!

96
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,279
When interests align,

97
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,600
people come together.

98
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,599
Now we're going to have new troubles.

99
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,200
Farewell.

100
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,839
Hahaha!

101
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,520
Chen Nan,

102
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,239
you'd better watch yourselves.

103
00:04:54,745 --> 00:04:55,656
Meng Ke'er,

104
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,039
Wait a second.

105
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,999
What’s there to say to that woman?

106
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,759
Your old friend asked me to pass on a message.

107
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,640
What message?

108
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,239
Let me think how it went...

109
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:14,759
A hundred times... a hundred times...

110
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,239
You...

111
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,240
You...

112
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,519
That damn rascal dragon!

113
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,439
Sooner or later, I’ll skin you alive!

114
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,679
He’s really learned some bad habits.

115
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,279
Looks like when it comes to framing me,

116
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,879
they’re all in perfect agreement for once.

117
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,600
Chen Nan,

118
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,599
Baby is so sleepy...

119
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,599
Alright.

120
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,879
Mmm...

121
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,480
What’s going on?

122
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,239
Wait!

123
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,399
Dragon Baby, don’t fall asleep!

124
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,279
Wake up!

125
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,359
Dragon Baby!

126
00:05:45,383 --> 00:06:04,983
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

127
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,719
That Eastern woman posted a letter outside the temple.

128
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,120
Please take a look.

129
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,119
Respected Grand Mage,

130
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,759
When the three of us first arrived,

131
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,999
we accidentally stumbled into the clash between the two churches

132
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,319
and unintentionally injured your temple mages.

133
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,200
To express our apology,

134
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:33,599
we captured the Dark Church mage who stole your holy relic.

135
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,639
The relic and the thief will be delivered to the temple by Chen Nan

136
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,520
as our way of making amends.

137
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,719
Looks like they’ve turned on each other.

138
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,599
The holy relic has fallen

139
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,799
into the hands of that young man named Chen Nan.

140
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,879
Should we send people to hunt him down?

141
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,680
No.

142
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:56,679
Both the man and the relic are in that youngster’s hands.

143
00:06:57,160 --> 00:07:00,239
The Dark Church is probably even more anxious than we are.

144
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,839
Spread the word.

145
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,159
Say that the Church of Light

146
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,599
is willing to let this misunderstanding go.

147
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,759
We will send someone to contact Chen Nan today.

148
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,039
Yes, sir.

149
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,679
Not bad. They’re quite clever.

150
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:25,199
They publicly posted this apology letter,

151
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:28,399
yet didn’t mention a single word about what the holy relic actually is.

152
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:31,959
At least they didn’t let the plan to resurrect the God of Light

153
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,479
become public knowledge.

154
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,280
My lord,

155
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,679
we’ve found the kidnapped experts.

156
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:49,079
The red-haired Easterner sent them back.

157
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,279
It says Chen Nan already killed the man.

158
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,080
The divine bone

159
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,719
is in Chen Nan’s hands.

160
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,199
You useless bunch!

161
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,679
Not only did you fail to steal the divine bone,

162
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,679
you’ve also brought shame upon the Dark Church!

163
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,759
For all your crimes combined,

164
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,479
receive your judgment!

165
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,679
Dragon Knight

166
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,319
Chen Nan.

167
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,719
Two fifth-tier experts behind him,

168
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,920
one in front,

169
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,119
and one hiding in the shadows.

170
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,839
I need to draw all these troublesome guys together

171
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,279
and finish them off at once.

172
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,319
Heaven Extinguishing Palm!

173
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,040
Young man,

174
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:39,799
I admire you for surviving

175
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,119
several days of pursuit by three fifth-tier experts.

176
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:42,719
Truly impressive.

177
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,559
Why not hand over the holy relic?

178
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,119
We can consider letting you leave.

179
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:49,960
What a joke.

180
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:53,399
You pinned that Dark Church mage’s death on me,

181
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,439
and these past few days I’ve made you lose even more men.

182
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,280
Let me go?

183
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:02,999
The Dark Church really has no face left to lose.

184
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
After him!

185
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:18,479
I wonder when Dragon Baby will wake up...

186
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,719
If I can’t get Xiang Tian’s Godfiend Wings later,

187
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:25,319
I’ll just have to try stealing Meng Ke’er’s Jade Lotus Platform instead.

188
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,239
They finally couldn’t hold back any longer.

189
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,080
Take him down!

190
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,239
You—

191
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,600
Get down!

192
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,919
Heaven and Earth Shaking!

193
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,999
I’ve been watching you for a while.

194
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,839
You’re quite good.

195
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,919
But your strength is running out,

196
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,399
and that little dragon has fallen into a coma.

197
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,479
You have no chance of escaping.

198
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,199
You’re wary of my Divine Spirit Dragon,

199
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,279
so you’ve been secretly observing

200
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:02,919
and hesitated to make a move.

201
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:04,920
But did you know...

202
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,639
I’ve been waiting for you to show yourself

203
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,160
for a very long time.

204
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,839
Every last one of you here

205
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,519
who wants to die—

206
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,039
come after me.

207
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:18,319
I’ve prepared a very special gift just for you.

208
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,200
How arrogant!

209
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,480
After him!

210
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,760
Chen Nan,

211
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,319
you have nowhere left to run.

212
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,319
Hand over that little creature and the divine bone.

213
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:14,159
At least then you can die with some dignity.

214
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,320
Attack!

215
00:13:20,160 --> 00:13:22,039
Hand over the divine bone! Hand it over!

216
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:26,039
Everyone’s here.

217
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,839
The terrain is perfect too.

218
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,400
Next up...

219
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:33,519
I hope you’re ready for the grand gift

220
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,279
I’ve prepared for all of you.

221
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,519
Heavenly Demon

222
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:38,920
Hand!

223
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:41,880
No!

224
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,679
Quick!

225
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:43,760
Stop him!

226
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,639
Four fifth-tier experts attacking at once...

227
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,599
Not even an immortal could escape that.

228
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,240
Ten days...

229
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:25,999
Is there any point in searching anymore?

230
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:33,559
What a shame... my dear prince.

231
00:15:14,221 --> 00:15:18,197
[Haoran Sect Seal: The Haoran Sect is a righteous force that once swept across all directions. It is said that the sect possesses divine-level seal techniques. The Haoran Sect Seal is one of its supreme techniques, capable of suppressing all things. When activated, it can gather the power of heaven and earth and seal everything within its domain. Once sealed, it is extremely difficult to break free.]

232
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:21,319
[Next Episode Preview]
The Church of Light has been loudly praising your deeds.

233
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,280
You’re completely famous now.

234
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:24,399
However...

235
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,720
let me remind you—

236
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:27,199
just because it’s called “Light”

237
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:28,400
doesn’t mean it’s actually bright.

238
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,480
This aura...

239
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,959
Why do you know my Chen family’s secret technique?

240
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,479
The Du family has inherited our legacy for ten thousand years.

241
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:42,719
We are the imperial sovereigns of the Eastern cultivation world.

242
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:43,800
Today,

243
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:46,799
I will eliminate you—the so-called number one of the younger generation!

244
00:15:46,823 --> 00:16:25,723
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

